\begin_layout Standard
This technical report defines the variables used in data sets that are collected
 by the research aircraft operated by the Research Aviation Facility (RAF)
 of the National Center for Atmospheric Research.
 Where appropriate, it also documents the equations that are used by the
 processing software (currently 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

nimbus
